    <item>
      <title>中国禁止出口部分稀土加工技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/china-bans-exports-of-some-rare-earth-processing-technologies-lqf1pzw8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将停止一系列稀土技术的出口，这可能会让美国和其他西方国家更难增加战略原材料的供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/china-bans-exports-of-some-rare-earth-processing-technologies-lqf1pzw8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利立法者拒绝批准ESM后备方案，对欧盟造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/italy-s-government-takes-stand-against-esm-backstop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利议会下院拒绝批准欧盟救助基金，从而拖延了与孤立意大利的欧盟伙伴的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/italy-s-government-takes-stand-against-esm-backstop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 09:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班认为欧盟国家在乌克兰援助问题上规避匈牙利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/orban-sees-eu-states-circumventing-hungary-on-aid-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟总理欧尔班·维克托周四表示，欧盟可以通过在明年初的峰会上与其他 26 个成员国达成一项单独协议，绕过匈牙利反对联合援助乌克兰的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/orban-sees-eu-states-circumventing-hungary-on-aid-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 09:48:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度备受争议的印度教寺庙为更多寺庙打开“闸门”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/india-s-controversial-hindu-temple-opens-floodgates-for-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪准备在一座有数百年历史的清真寺所在地开设一座有争议的印度教寺庙，印度教团体在过去一周赢得了法院对其他有争议的宗教场所的重要裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/india-s-controversial-hindu-temple-opens-floodgates-for-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
